Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.50,0:00:04.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.61,0:00:07.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Son of a bitch, this ain't funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.08,0:00:11.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.15,0:00:15.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you fool me, Rapowant?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.69,0:00:16.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Byro...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.47,0:02:18.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu! Thank goodness you're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.43,0:02:20.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.03,0:02:22.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You think I'd be done in by \Nthe likes of these chumps?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.72,0:02:25.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy, treat the cardinal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.13,0:02:25.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.89,0:02:27.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This person is a cardinal?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.26,0:02:30.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.19,0:02:34.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You even dare break into this holy \Nsanctuary? I've never seen a more insolent guild...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.44,0:02:35.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Byro...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.37,0:02:36.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.82,0:02:44.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how desperately you maggots \Nstruggle, you won't be able to stop Real Nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.90,0:02:47.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This world is going to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.01,0:02:52.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The great power behind the \Nestablishment of Zentopia,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.02,0:02:54.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,its source is the Infinity Clock...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.35,0:02:58.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago, it was called the Infinity Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.60,0:03:00.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Infinity Castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.92,0:03:04.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,During the upcoming anniversary event \Nthat's held once every 100 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.00,0:03:09.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the Infinity Castle will release \Nall of the magic it's accumulated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.49,0:03:11.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,100 years' worth of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.30,0:03:13.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no way to fight against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:16.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you doing this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.16,0:03:19.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To return this world to chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.35,0:03:21.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no other reason than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.24,0:03:24.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I control Real Nightmare,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.82,0:03:29.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can return the world to the state of chaos \Nit was in prior to the founding of Zentopia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.00,0:03:34.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The time has come for people to unleash the \Nmalice and desires they've kept sealed deep inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:36.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what Neville feared,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.00,0:03:39.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,which is why he created a seal that \Nwould last throughout the ages, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.43,0:03:41.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But what does that have to do with Lucy-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.83,0:03:46.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To the Infinity Castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.27,0:03:52.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Girl who holds most of the 12 Gold Keys,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:56.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,who opens the gates to other worlds, \Nyou possess a high level of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.41,0:04:00.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This clock that was sealed away \Nby Celestial Spirit Wizards
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.21,0:04:04.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,can only be controlled by the magic \Nof a Celestial Spirit Wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.62,0:04:05.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you expect to do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.25,0:04:10.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Relax. You're just a sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.17,0:04:12.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The clock is in our possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.77,0:04:17.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Through your magic, the Infinity Castle \Nwill be in tune with our intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.99,0:04:23.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With Real Nightmare, individual \Nvalues are controlled,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:27.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and as a result, discord will \Ndisappear from the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:28.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:32.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-san, you're going to \Ngive people true freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.28,0:04:36.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wish to stop the Infinity Clock,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.13,0:04:38.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll have to put an \Nend to that girl's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.24,0:04:40.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.65,0:04:44.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The end of the world will \Nstart here, from Zentopia!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:50.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.00,0:04:52.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My body...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.61,0:04:54.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I pity you, Rapowant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.17,0:04:58.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.87,0:05:01.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're also one of the fakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.81,0:05:06.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't realize that you were just a \Npuppet, created by Personification Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:10.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who used that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.22,0:05:11.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What nonsense are you talking...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.85,0:05:15.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've seen a lot of puppets on our way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.52,0:05:19.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They had the same form as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:20.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.24,0:05:23.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You were merely a tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.01,0:05:25.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.01,0:05:27.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a Zentopia cardinal!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.64,0:05:30.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not... a doll...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.45,0:05:34.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.36,0:05:37.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That smell...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:39.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Zero's hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:41.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pathetic thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:44.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it was made to think it was human.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.58,0:05:46.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just Rapowant...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.73,0:05:51.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My Legion was also nothing more than tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.76,0:05:55.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But at last, I've realized \Nthe path I should take.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:06:01.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As Zentopia's soldiers, \Nwe should save the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.29,0:06:04.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to stop the Infinity Clock,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.99,0:06:06.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will dispose of Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:08.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Over my dead body!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.00,0:06:15.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.11,0:06:19.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a score to even with this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.57,0:06:22.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest of you save Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.55,0:06:26.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I wanna pay this \Nguy back 100 times over,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.24,0:06:28.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'll let you take him, Gildarts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.38,0:06:31.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know how to get to the Infinity Castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.83,0:06:34.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Lead on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.38,0:06:36.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Coco... I'm glad you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.12,0:06:39.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.86,0:06:41.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sammy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:44.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall carry out Byro-sama's will.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.21,0:06:45.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talkin' about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.78,0:06:47.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.40,0:06:50.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nii-san, this is my decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.52,0:06:52.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Already, there's no time to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.00,0:06:53.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Sammy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:06:56.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel bad for all of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:06:59.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't need to calculate to know this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:02.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When one life is in the balance \Nagainst the end of the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.89,0:07:04.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the answer is obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.31,0:07:05.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.34,0:07:07.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.60,0:07:08.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:11.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:13.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:16.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that {\i1}I'm{\i0} your opponent!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.19,0:07:20.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu! Please save Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:21.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.85,0:07:22.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.26,0:07:25.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Warren, you stay here as \Nour communications liaison.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.77,0:07:28.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray, Gajeel, Elfman, come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.69,0:07:29.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.59,0:07:31.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.01,0:07:32.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you take your eyes off of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.00,0:07:36.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.80,0:07:40.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have the power to nullify all magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.25,0:07:43.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't use magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.91,0:07:46.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,then I guess I'll just \Nhave to rely on this, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:49.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In a physical showdown,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:54.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I, who practice swordplay and barehanded \Nfighting every day, will surely win.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.01,0:08:02.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're big on logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.15,0:08:09.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:12.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...I have you on the defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.01,0:08:17.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that Rapowant \Nis no longer with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.13,0:08:20.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,His role was already done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.88,0:08:24.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Although he was a puppet \Nmade from my father's hair,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.04,0:08:25.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,in the end, he was disposable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.72,0:08:27.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.06,0:08:30.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if you create it from \Nmagic or what, but a life is a life!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.92,0:08:31.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Incorrect.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.86,0:08:34.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's important is the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.14,0:08:37.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what that {\i1}thing{\i0} was lacking in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:39.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.86,0:08:45.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it the same magic that was cast on Cana?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.06,0:08:46.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.26,0:08:49.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Wendy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.78,0:08:51.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My Healing Magic has no effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.62,0:08:52.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:55.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,His fever hasn't gone down either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.46,0:08:56.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.66,0:09:00.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are traces of magic on the archbishop's \Nbrain, showing he was under a spell for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.05,0:09:02.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's clinging to him like a disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.41,0:09:06.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless it can be removed, the \Narchbishop won't recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.76,0:09:08.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.92,0:09:13.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can perform delicate Healing Magic \Nupon him without damaging his brain...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.19,0:09:15.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If the archbishop returns to his senses,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.85,0:09:18.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,we may be able to learn something \Nabout the Infinity Clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:21.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you best, Wendy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:22.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.43,0:09:26.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's coming closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.44,0:09:28.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it Natsu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:29.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No... This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:33.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I found you! My calculations were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.32,0:09:35.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... Samuel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.11,0:09:38.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy-nee-san belongs to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.52,0:09:40.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let anyone else have her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.66,0:09:43.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Samuel on your side, Michelle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.84,0:09:46.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That may have been the case once.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.46,0:09:48.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I know why he's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.36,0:09:50.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He intends to kill you, Nee-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.29,0:10:09.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I made an error...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.83,0:10:12.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's ironic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:19.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We used Legion and now you're after \Nher life, while we're protecting her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.77,0:10:26.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I can't fly...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.30,0:10:28.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can use my own legs to climb.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.32,0:10:31.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Byro-sama... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.21,0:10:39.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You could hear their telepathic \Ncommunications, too, couldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.98,0:10:42.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you intend to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.39,0:10:44.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.78,0:10:50.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Byro-sama... Even His Grace, the \Narchbishop himself, was just used as a tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.55,0:10:52.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.20,0:10:55.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...so were you and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:11:02.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it wasn't Zentopia's doctrine. I was \Njust being used by the new Oracion Seis.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.69,0:11:04.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:07.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like such a loser...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.68,0:11:13.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gatman-chama... Gatman-chama...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.27,0:11:18.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...will shut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.26,0:11:20.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.82,0:11:22.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.69,0:11:27.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest is up to you... Coco...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.79,0:11:30.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.15,0:11:32.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl is fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.20,0:11:33.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,According to Fabrizio-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.71,0:11:36.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,we can get up to the Infinity Castle
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.06,0:11:40.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,through the eye at the triangle \Nof the cathedral's center!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.35,0:11:42.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.20,0:11:58.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Lahar, the Captain of the Enforcement \Nand Detention Corps of the Magic Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.24,0:12:01.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you're inside this \Nbarrier that the Rune Knights made,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.44,0:12:04.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,you won't be influenced by the \Nmagic coming from those chains.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.04,0:12:08.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay quiet in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.13,0:12:09.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Direct Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:12.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:14.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.14,0:12:16.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to take you inside this barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:19.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead, quickly! Inside the barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.84,0:12:23.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.91,0:12:26.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,His complexion is improving little by little.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.17,0:12:28.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carefully...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.75,0:12:30.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Delicately...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.96,0:12:33.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks tough...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.76,0:12:36.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time she's tried \Nto cure someone continuously
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.56,0:12:37.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,over the course of several hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.31,0:12:43.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gildarts Clive!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.90,0:12:50.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you giving me \Neverything you've got?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.36,0:12:54.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want the brats to see it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.16,0:12:59.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Me pulverizing you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.44,0:13:01.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You jest with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:03.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a good warming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:22.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This might be good once in a while, \Npitting muscles against muscles.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.86,0:13:33.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy, if you go overboard, \Nit'll put you in danger, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.61,0:13:35.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you take a little break?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.61,0:13:39.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine. It's finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.84,0:13:40.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.99,0:13:44.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! When did you improve this much?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.91,0:13:47.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've just gained experience, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.22,0:13:52.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, the archbishop has \Nbeen freed from that magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.46,0:13:56.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true! His fever's down, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.32,0:13:57.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are some impressive skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.86,0:13:59.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We sure can rely on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.66,0:14:04.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She removed the magic, which \Nsaved the archbishop's life...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.16,0:14:06.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She removed it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.58,0:14:07.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.35,0:14:08.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.17,0:14:14.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Samuel is going to try stopping \Nthe clock by eliminating Lucy,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.01,0:14:16.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but there's another way to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.73,0:14:18.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.31,0:14:21.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We beat all the members \Nof the new Oracion Seis!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.56,0:14:23.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The members of the new Oracion Seis?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.75,0:14:25.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Beat {\i1}all{\i0} of them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.19,0:14:26.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What would that do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.72,0:14:31.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When the Infinity Clock was reactivated, the new \NOracion Seis engraved their seals on it, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.81,0:14:42.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When I think back, I remember \NMichelle engraving the sixth seal...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.30,0:14:49.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those seals must serve as proof of \Nownership of the Infinity Clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.93,0:14:52.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So if we defeat all the members \Nof the new Oracion Seis,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:55.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,we can remove their right of ownership \Nto the Infinity Clock, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.76,0:14:58.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And then maybe we'll be \Nable to free Lucy, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.47,0:14:59.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.13,0:15:02.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! I'll pass that on to \NNatsu and the others right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.95,0:15:05.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna set off to find Lucy, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.24,0:15:06.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.42,0:15:10.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay here with Wendy, \Nbut be careful, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:13.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Did everyone catch that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.79,0:15:15.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Infinity Clock...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.99,0:15:17.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hear so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.83,0:15:20.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There was lots of static, but it's \Na telepathic message from Warren!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.25,0:15:22.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.18,0:15:25.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we beat all the members \Nof the new Oracion Seis...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.01,0:15:27.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...we'll be able to stop the Infinity Clock?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.26,0:15:29.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And we might be able to \Nsave Lucy that way, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.89,0:15:31.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I like how easy it is to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.51,0:15:34.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All we have to do is kick \Nall their asses, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.72,0:15:37.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A simple strategy that stirs up the blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.44,0:15:39.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now {\i1}that's{\i0} a Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.36,0:15:41.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.38,0:15:43.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.73,0:15:46.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.15,0:15:46.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cobra?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.32,0:15:48.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.89,0:15:52.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your anxiety, desperation, despair...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.15,0:15:54.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna take him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.79,0:15:57.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.19,0:15:59.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Before that, there's someone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.87,0:16:02.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...I want to finish off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.15,0:16:09.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard him, right? I think he likes me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.00,0:16:10.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.26,0:16:13.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard them...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:15.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The screams from his heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.60,0:16:16.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.15,0:16:18.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.81,0:16:19.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.05,0:16:23.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza! If you lose, I'm gonna wallop you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.81,0:16:26.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you laughing about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.31,0:16:29.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not even worth answering.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:31.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can hear it, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.88,0:16:35.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.47,0:16:36.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A greenhouse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.46,0:16:39.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would somethin' like \Nthat be inside a clock?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.17,0:16:40.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How the hell should I know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.76,0:16:44.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's as far as you go, cretins.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.89,0:16:47.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:49.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Angel...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.86,0:16:51.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.23,0:16:54.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?! Everybody's \Ndecidin' on their own!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.52,0:16:55.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter, just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.78,0:16:57.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.17,0:16:58.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She kind of annoys me, anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:02.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Boring...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:03.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to fight you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.26,0:17:05.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.81,0:17:07.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make it interesting for you soon enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.88,0:17:17.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I discovered an intruder!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:19.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Midnight!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.17,0:17:22.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean... Brain II, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.09,0:17:26.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not letting you people \Nget any higher than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:29.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! I'll take this guy on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.99,0:17:32.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get cocky, Salamander!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:35.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This one's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.01,0:17:38.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Gajeel?! You're \Nthe one that's cocky!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:42.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you call yourself Brain II,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.29,0:17:46.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,that means you're the leader \Nof the new Oracion Seis, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.44,0:17:49.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're a Fairy Tail underling, I take it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.11,0:17:51.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You better find that out for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.72,0:17:53.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get outta here, Salamander!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.54,0:17:56.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, don't decide by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.37,0:18:00.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leaving this one in Gajeel's \Nhands and pressing on is a Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.23,0:18:01.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.63,0:18:03.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll remember this, asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.78,0:18:11.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.33,0:18:14.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Spicy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:16.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sugar Boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.32,0:18:18.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You still intend to fight us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.37,0:18:25.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Byro-sama ordered me to keep Fairy Tail \Naway from the Infinity Clock, see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.03,0:18:27.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Armor Girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.34,0:18:29.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Circumstances have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.45,0:18:33.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, Byro and the new \NOracion Seis are enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.64,0:18:37.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.85,0:18:40.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true, Snake Boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.46,0:18:41.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.85,0:18:42.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.96,0:18:44.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Be destroyed by your own voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:53.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...?! I'm losing control \Nof my hound dogs! No!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.49,0:18:53.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of my sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.02,0:18:55.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.31,0:18:57.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so excited about \Nfighting Ice Boy again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.74,0:19:06.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But before that, fade out! Spicy! \NBye-bye, Armor Girl and Snake Boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.51,0:19:11.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, let's continue, Titania.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.45,0:19:15.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lance of the Iron Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.35,0:19:20.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So you're a Dragon Slayer, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.54,0:19:25.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Reflector or whatever it's \Ncalled? That kinda magic is annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.23,0:19:28.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one they call Iron Gajeel, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.04,0:19:30.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like your brain's \Nmade out of iron, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.62,0:19:31.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.75,0:19:34.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lance of the Iron Dragon... Demon Logs!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.16,0:19:42.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I get more powerful when I eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.07,0:19:46.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar of the Iron Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.84,0:19:57.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've made me want to see your \Nface... when you're in agony.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.14,0:20:02.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how twisted up my face gets, as \Nlong as I don't run away, who gives a shit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.00,0:20:04.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sword of the Iron Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.79,0:20:12.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you in was the rarely-seen...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.50,0:20:13.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Spiral Pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.50,0:20:23.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come at me with more power!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.06,0:20:26.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all there is?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.00,0:20:28.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me everything you got!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.99,0:20:39.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too wide...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.86,0:20:42.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The gap between our strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.37,0:20:45.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You got beyond the frustration \Nof being betrayed
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.02,0:20:48.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and fought for what you believe in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.41,0:20:50.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But the thing is,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.69,0:20:54.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,to our guild, there's nothin' more \Nimportant than the lives of our friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.07,0:20:58.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the fate of the \Nworld is in the balance...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.44,0:21:05.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to fight with you longer,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.64,0:21:07.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.07,0:21:15.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Goddammit! I was just gettin' started!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.93,0:21:16.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.00,0:21:19.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.98,0:21:25.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.00,0:21:33.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The hub of the magic power that \Nflows through the Infinity Castle...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.90,0:21:35.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We should be close to it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.95,0:21:38.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't smell Lucy's scent. Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.60,0:21:42.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's because she's linked \Nup to the Infinity Clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.94,0:21:44.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm picking up Michelle's scent!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.44,0:21:48.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we follow that, it could lead us to Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.19,0:21:49.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.23,0:21:56.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.10,0:22:02.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.36,0:22:03.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elfman...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.59,0:22:04.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Coco...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.67,0:22:09.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-san's never going back to you people.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.51,0:22:12.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All Nee-san needs is me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.41,0:22:15.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Michelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.07,0:22:18.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let anyone have Nee-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.67,0:23:58.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I guess \Nan angel appeared this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.13,0:24:01.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An angel? Aren't angels creatures \Nfrom fantasy stories?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.84,0:24:03.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.50,0:24:05.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but I saw with my own eyes, \Nso what do you want me to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.17,0:24:08.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, maybe you're talking about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.44,0:24:10.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How the hell could you take \Nwhat I said to mean that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.29,0:24:14.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When you say "Fairy Tail" and "angel" \Ntogether, you must be referring to me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.41,0:24:16.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: An Angel's Tears!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.77,0:24:19.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Since when has anyone \Nidentified you as an angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.57,0:24:22.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe since the day I was born...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.43,0:24:24.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you can say \Nthat with a straight face.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.53,0:24:26.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
